## Scenario 2

A large hospital network’s IT department notices unusual activity late at night. 

When doctors arrive in the morning, they can’t access patient records, lab results, or appointment systems. 

All hospital monitors display the same note: 
“Your files have been encrypted. Pay $5 million in Bitcoin within 72 hours or all data will be lost.”

&nbsp;

<img src="https://images.code.org/b16c76b9403264fc2940faf2fab6b73b-image-1752764768757.05.25 AM.png" alt="computer monitor locked with a price tag" width="300"/>
